snippet.title: Shera & the 40 Thieves (A New NES Game!)
snippet.description:
Available on Kickstarter! ►http://kck.st/3yujdPZ
Shera & the 40 Thieves is a new NES game made by me! The game is available as a physical cartridge for a limited time as well as digital. Check it out!
Patreon ► http://bit.ly/cgtpatreon
Metroid Ascension ► https://fanlink.to/cgtMetroidAD
Best of Donkey Kong Country ►  https://fanlink.to/CGTDKC

Spotify ► http://bit.ly/ZFrI8U
iTunes ► http://bit.ly/1yhsR2F

Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/crazygrouptrio
Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/crazygrouptrio
